data.title: Brewster McCloud
data.text:
1970, Rated R, 101 min. Directed by Robert Altman. Starring Bud Cort, Shelley Duvall, Michael Murphy and Sally Kellerman.

Texas Film Awards Screening: On the eve of the 20th annual Texas Film Awards, see the Houston-shot film that will receive the Star of Texas Award. Stars Shelley Duvall and Michael Murphy will appear at this special Star of Texas screening.

6406 N. I-35 Ste. 3100, 512/322-0145
